statements: SELECT ROUND(Median(unitPrice), 3) AS median, count(*) AS cnt FROM product WHERE test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Median(DISTINCT unitPrice) FROM product WHERE test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT ROUND(Median(DISTINCT unitPrice), 0) FROM product WHERE test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Median(orderInfo.qty) from orders UNNEST orderlines AS orderInfo WHERE orders.test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Median(DISTINCT orderInfo.qty) from orders UNNEST orderlines AS orderInfo WHERE orders.test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Stddev(orderInfo.qty) from orders UNNEST orderlines AS orderInfo WHERE orders.test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Stddev(DISTINCT orderInfo.qty) from orders UNNEST orderlines AS orderInfo WHERE orders.test_id = "agg_func"
SELECT Stddev(cntn) FROM orders WHERE cntn=10 and test_id = "cntn_agg_func"
SELECT Stddev(DISTINCT cntn) FROM orders WHERE cntn=10 and test_id = "cntn_agg_func"
SELECT count(*) from product WHERE test_id = "agg_func"
